description:
English Version
Louis Vuitton Manufactures illustrates the idea, fostered by the House, that a manufacture can be a place of fulfillment and individuality, where traditional craft skills can be learned, respected and transmitted, using age-old techniques and tools that would be familiar to the company‚Äôs founder. In pursuit of excellence, Louis Vuitton has scattered ateliers the length and breadth of France and beyond, to Geneva, the Veneto and even Texas. Often sites of historic interest or outstanding natural beauty will have a Louis Vuitton workshop nearby. Featuring exclusively commissioned photographs, this magnificent volume showcases the extraordinary locations and buildings, and the equally extraordinary artisans, that produce Louis Vuitton leather goods, fragrances, watches, shoes, high jewelry and ready-to-wear.
10 x 13 inches / 25 x 33 cm

description:
For sale is a pair of 2000 Louis Vuitton Cup rimless sunglasses. From 1983-2017, the prestigious Louis Vuitton sponsored event was one of the world‚Äôs first clashes of luxury goods and sporting gear. The requirement for performance focused gear in this boat racing competition not only served as a display of wealth for labels, but was a way to advertise their brands on a televised global scale.
Louis Vuitton‚Äôs 2000 Cup team uniform featured these beautiful rimless visor sunglasses. Featuring a sleek silver frame with LV branding etched into the side of each arm, these shades are complemented by deep blue mirrored lenses. This heavily performance focused shape has been built to endure the test of time and celebrates the first worldwide sporting event of the third millennium. In pristine overall condition with hardly any wear, here is the opportunity to purchase a rare pair of 2000 Louis Vuitton Cup rimless sunglasses.
